    				Contenxt Search    			 
  			 
    			 Search has used content for quite some time ‚Äî in pure text, databases, and multimedia.  Lately application of context has started receiving increasing attention. 
The real progress could be made if we really combine content and context.  Approaches should be developed that are really both content and context based.  I think we should start using ‚Äòcontenxt‚Äô to describe use of both content and context in search. 
  			 
  			 	        			
    			 
